---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About LearnGen and Ian Melchor">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text);">About</h1>

    <p class="mb-4 text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text);">
      I'm Ian. <strong>Technical Product Manager</strong>, <strong>generalist</strong>, <strong>builder</strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text);">
      I write about <strong>AI orchestration</strong>, <strong>product development</strong>, and what it looks like when generalists stop apologizing and start winning.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: var(--color-code-bg); color: var(--color-text);">
      <strong>The bet:</strong> in the AI age, the person who orchestrates tools and synthesizes domains beats the specialist.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text);">
      Before tech, I spent a decade as a loan officer. It shows in how I build - <strong>domain expertise first</strong>, then tools to serve it.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text);">
      This blog is where the <strong>overflow</strong> goes. What I'm building, what I'm learning, what's working.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text);">
      Based in Denver.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-8 border-t" style="border-color: var(--color-border);" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text);">Outside of work</h2>

    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text);">
      <li>Partner: <strong>Haley</strong>. Son: <strong>Liam</strong>.</li>
      <li>Budding <strong>coffee enthusiast</strong> - we make our own at home together.</li>
      <li><strong>Acoustic guitar</strong> and open mics when I can. You might see the occasional video here.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/VindiceCode"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-sm"
        style="color: var(--color-accent);"
      >
        GitHub
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ian-melchor-a270b27b/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-sm"
        style="color: var(--color-accent);"
      >
        LinkedIn
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
